I"D<p>This post is a walkthrough for having <a href="https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-neopixel-uberguide">neopixels</a> (individually addressable LEDs) flash in firefly patterns.  The script uses <a href="https://circuitpython.org/">circuitpython</a> and uses three flash patterns from a National Park Service <a href="https://www.nps.gov/grsm/learn/nature/firefly-flash-patterns.htm">website</a>.  It should be very easy to add additional patterns as you see fit.  The full script can be found <a href="https://github.com/mwweinberg/firefly/blob/master/firefly.py">here</a>.</p>
